  <h2>5. CSS Styling Highlights</h2>
  <p>The website is styled using custom CSS. Key styling elements are shown below:</p>
  <pre><code>
:root {
  --main-color: #4CAF50;
  --font: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
}

body {
  font-family: var(--font);
  background-color: #fff;
  color: #333;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

a:hover {
  color: var(--main-color);
}
  </code></pre>

  <h2>6. Changes Made to Template</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Refactored layout to use semantic HTML5 structure (`section`, `article`, `nav`).</li>
    <li>Improved accessibility (added `aria-label`, keyboard navigation, contrast ratios).</li>
    <li>Removed unused scripts and CSS for performance.</li>
    <li>Added responsive navbar with toggler for mobile.</li>
  </ul>

